@Joel Palmer You can switch to wednesdays or Thursdays then not an issue.
@Joel Palmer I try to get the triaging report in by 12 AM GMT on Monday...

John Simon said:

Joel Palmer I try to get the triaging report in by 12 AM GMT on Monday...

You dont have to, a report at any time during your day is fine even if it crosses UTC day timings.
